        {
            "title": "魚樂無窮│順豐同城盈利倍升 受惠平台公平競爭要求（唐牛）",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"順豐同城公佈全年業績，截至去年底止收入增長45%至229億元人民幣，期內盈利增長1.1倍至2.78億元人民幣。\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/COnslGRQj98ATQzpiGjeQA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-12/a84dea60-db5f-11f0-bbf7-8071c99affe8\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"順豐同城\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:順豐同城;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/順豐同城\">順豐同城</a>公佈全年業績，截至去年底止收入增長45%至229億元<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"人民幣\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:人民幣;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/人民幣\">人民幣</a>，期內盈利增長1.1倍至2.78億元人民幣。</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">順豐同城（9699.HK）公佈全年業績，截至去年底止收入增長45%至229億元人民幣，期內盈利增長1.1倍至2.78億元人民幣，經調整盈利增幅更達1.8倍，至4.15億元人民幣，顯示其在即時配送行業中，持續保持高增長及盈利能力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link rapid-with-clickid etailiffa-link athena-button\" data-i13n=\"sec:shop-now;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Yahoo;elmt:other;pdid:\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"1\",\"yLinkElement\":\"affiliate_link\",\"yAffiliateService\":\"other\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"shop-now\",\"ySellerName\":\"Yahoo\",\"yLinkText\":\"下載Yahoo財經APP\",\"yHasCommerce\":true}' data-ylk=\"slk:下載Yahoo財經APP;sec:shop-now;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Yahoo;elmt:other;pdid:;itc:0\" href=\"https://mobile.yahoo.com/finance?pid=editorial&amp;c=HK_Acquisition_YMktg_Evergreen_article_&amp;af_sub1=Acquisition&amp;af_sub2=HK_YMktg&amp;af_sub4=1058&amp;af_sub5=article__Banner_\">下載Yahoo財經APP</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>美股外幣即時報價 多國新聞任睇</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">事實上，集團全場景能力已構成護城河，面向商家（To B）的同城配送服務收入增長60%至107億元人民幣，面向消費者（To C）的同城配送服務收入則升14%至28億元人民幣，最後一公里配送服務收入增長42%至94億元人民幣，三者均見健康成長動力。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-00637672-5252-45a1-9f64-2495f8f12053-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">國務院反壟斷委員會已正式啟動對外賣平台「拼補貼、控流量」等問題的調查，令平台行業從「平台強勢壓費率」轉向「公平競爭」。從中長線角度出發，隨着商家話語權回歸，第三方即配運力的重要性進一步提升，順豐同城作為市場少有的第三方平台，承接全渠道訂單，有望直接受惠於即時零售需求帶動即配訂單高增長的局面。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">從估值角度出發，順豐同城現價市銷率約0.47倍，較美團市銷率約1.3倍，以及行業平均約1倍有明顯折讓，變相有追落後空間。如能守穩近期低位10元水平，博反彈有一定值博率，不妨留意。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">散聚有時，魚樂無窮專欄今日在Yahoo財經正式畫上句號。在此感謝Yahoo財經團隊上上下下一直以來的關顧及厚愛，後會有期！</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">唐牛</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%AD%9A%E6%A8%82%E7%84%A1%E7%AA%AE%E2%94%82%E9%A0%86%E8%B1%90%E5%90%8C%E5%9F%8E%E7%9B%88%E5%88%A9%E5%80%8D%E5%8D%87-%E5%8F%97%E6%83%A0%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%E5%85%AC%E5%B9%B3%E7%AB%B6%E7%88%AD%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%88%E5%94%90%E7%89%9B%EF%BC%89-000010788.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-31 09:39:00",
