        {
            "title": "日本外匯主管警告將採取「大膽」行動 日圓應聲小幅反彈",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"Photographer: Shoko Takayasu/Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/bXXq.z67mEMRT.VNM756oA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/932abe7ee75b4c1fca99c4c124f81321\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Photographer: Shoko Takayasu/Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 日本最高貨幣官員向投機者發出了迄今為止最嚴厲的警告，稱如果當前狀況持續，當局可能需要在外匯市場採取大膽行動。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日本外匯事務負責人三村淳周一告訴記者：「我們聽到越來越多的擔憂，即投機活動不僅在原油期貨市場，而且在外匯市場也在增加。」他表示：「如果這種情況持續下去，我們認為可能很快需要採取大膽行動。」</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"Photographer: Shoko Takayasu/Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/BzjwLFBu4LK1KbOdZBg9PQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/edc17dfb06cdc60ce3ae0259b5c12cf1\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Photographer: Shoko Takayasu/Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">三村淳發表上述言論之前，日圓兌美元在周末前已一度跌破160關口，而2024年日本曾在此水平進行過干預。在三村淳表態以及當天晚些時候財務大臣片山皋月講話後，日圓從此前一度跌至160.46回升至159.33，隨後漲幅收窄。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-fc72928f-86e8-3e72-b525-97c9d572f246-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我們準備在所有方面作出回應，我們的關注範圍廣泛且全面，」他說，暗示政府不僅在監控外匯市場，也在關注原油期貨市場。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">雖然片山皋月自去年年底以來多次提及可能採取「大膽行動」——這一表述通常被廣泛理解為干預的信號——但三村淳自2024年7月就任以來尚未使用過該詞。日本外匯事務負責人發表的此類言論通常被視為在實際干預以支撐日圓之前發出的最後警告。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">片山皋月周一在七國集團財長和能源部長會議上重申日本對匯率走勢的關切。她表示，原油期貨波動正波及匯市。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「已發展到影響實體經濟和民眾日常生活的程度，」她在G7線上會議後的新聞發布會上表示。「因此我明確表示，我們正以非常高的緊迫感關注市場動態。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Japan’s Latest Warnings on FX Intervention Help Buoy Yen (2)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Yen Edges Away From Weakest Since 2024 Amid Intervention Risk</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">(新增日本財務大臣講話、日圓走勢)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"1\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
