            "title": "財經｜贛鋒鋰業(01772)全年虧轉盈賺16.14億元人民幣",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"財經｜贛鋒鋰業(01772)全年虧轉盈賺16.14億元人民幣\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">財經｜贛鋒鋰業(01772)全年虧轉盈賺16.14億元人民幣</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">贛鋒鋰業(01772)公布，截至去年12月底止全年業績，營業額227.98億元人民幣(下同)，按年升21.7%。虧轉盈賺16.14億元，上年同期蝕20.69億元；每股盈利0.8元。派末期息0.15元，上年同期派0.15元。</p></div>",
